@startuml
actor User
participant SPA
participant AuthController
participant AuthService
database TokenRepo
database SessionRepo
queue Outbox

User -> SPA : request password reset
SPA -> AuthController : POST /auth/forgot-password
AuthController -> AuthService : create reset request
AuthService -> TokenRepo : store hashed token if user exists
AuthService -> Outbox : enqueue reset email
AuthController --> SPA : 202 accepted
User -> SPA : submit token + new password
SPA -> AuthController : POST /auth/reset-password
AuthController -> AuthService : reset password
AuthService -> SessionRepo : revoke all sessions
AuthController --> SPA : 200 success
@enduml
